Managing .pacnew files

Manual: https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Pacman/Pacnew_and_Pacsave

Using Pacdiff to manage pacnew files:

Find files with
$ sudo pacdiff -f

Merge with (M)

When in Vimdiff use the following commands:
]c & [c = cycle though changes
do = diff obtain
dp = diff put
dd = delete line
u  = undo
qa!= force quit all dont save

Grabing particular lines only:
Use the mouse and highlight the text you want to add and
$ :diffput

When done save and quit the base file with:
$ :wq

Quit the other side with:
$ :q
